- Go on, get out of here!
- Evil spirit, begone!

00:09:41.956 --> 00:09:43.249 position:50% align:center
- The heck, Mom?
- Kiriko!

00:09:43.333 --> 00:09:44.834 position:50% align:center
- Dammit people, don't you know
you're gonna face

00:09:44.918 --> 00:09:46.670 position:50% align:center
