00:09:56.638 --> 00:09:58.890 position:50% align:center
- Yeah, I'll see you over there.
- Yeah.

00:09:58.973 --> 00:10:01.101 position:50% align:center
- Take care of yourself, Shu.
- Thanks for helping back there!

00:10:01.184 --> 00:10:02.560 position:50% align:center
- Really, thanks, Shu!
- It's nothing!

00:10:02.644 --> 00:10:04.604 position:50% align:center
- I tell ya,
