[hip-hop music]

00:10:15.031 --> 00:10:21.621 position:50% align:center
- [humming]

00:10:21.705 --> 00:10:23.665 position:50% align:center
Ah.
[giggles]

00:10:23.748 --> 00:10:26.835 position:50% align:center
[grunts]
And finished!

00:10:27.502 --> 00:10:30.088 position:50% align:center
I present to you
our new graffiti.

00:10:30.171 --> 00:10:32.882 position:50% align:center
This new piece of street art
from the one and only DoRed

00:10:32.966 --> 00:10:35.218 position:50% align:center
