- Kaba and Mari meddle

00:18:03.625 --> 00:18:05.293 position:50% align:center
in other people's business
too much.

00:18:05.377 --> 00:18:07.128 position:50% align:center
- You're letting Mari spoil you
too much.

00:18:07.212 --> 00:18:08.838 position:50% align:center
- Gotta admit, I agree.

