Elementary School fire.

00:18:19.474 --> 00:18:20.975 position:50% align:center
- [grunts]
- Huh?

00:18:21.059 --> 00:18:23.228 position:50% align:center
Oh, no.
Is that Kozue?

00:18:23.311 --> 00:18:24.396 position:50% align:center
- Don't worry, darling.

00:18:24.479 --> 00:18:25.855 position:50% align:center
You're almost at
the medical office.

00:18:25.939 --> 00:18:27.732 position:50% align:center
Just a bit farther.
- Okay.

00:18:27.816 --> 00:18:29.442 position:50% align:center
Oh, no Shuta!
I'm so sorry!

00:18:29.526 --> 00:18:30.985 position:50% align:center
Please forgive me!

00:18:33.780 --> 00:18:35.407 position:50% align:center
