00:18:35.490 --> 00:18:37.075 position:50% align:center
but I've got an emergency
at the moment,

00:18:37.158 --> 00:18:38.618 position:50% align:center
so could you kill some time
for me?

00:18:38.702 --> 00:18:40.787 position:50% align:center
- Hey, no problem,
but is she--

00:18:40.870 --> 00:18:42.414 position:50% align:center
- Is somethin' the matter
with Kozue?

00:18:42.497 --> 00:18:44.457 position:50% align:center
- You saw all that, huh?

00:18:45.166 --> 00:18:47.335 position:50% align:center
- I had heard some rumors
