00:18:56.428 --> 00:18:57.887 position:50% align:center
Sorry about all this.

00:18:57.971 --> 00:18:59.264 position:50% align:center
You guys are victims as well

00:18:59.347 --> 00:19:01.099 position:50% align:center
but I'm making
you be considerate.

00:19:01.182 --> 00:19:04.436 position:50% align:center
