because it was a memorial mass.

00:19:04.519 --> 00:19:06.062 position:50% align:center
I suppose that was a mistake.

00:19:06.146 --> 00:19:07.814 position:50% align:center
- No way.
Of course it isn't.

00:19:07.897 --> 00:19:10.942 position:50% align:center
It's just a bit complicated
with Kozue, right?

00:19:11.026 --> 00:19:13.403 position:50% align:center
I think I understand
how she feels.

00:19:13.486 --> 00:19:14.571 position:50% align:center
- [chuckles]

00:19:14.654 --> 00:19:16.156 position:50% align:center
So with all that said,

00:19:16.239 --> 00:19:18.158 position:50% align:center
I want to be by Kozue's side
for a bit.

00:19:18.241 --> 00:19:20.035 position:50% align:center
I'll text you when
she settles down.

00:19:21.453 --> 00:19:23.621 position:50% align:center
- What you guys gonna do?
- If I have time,

00:19:23.705 --> 00:19:25.248 position:50% align:center
I would like to take care
of several items

00:19:25.331 --> 00:19:26.875 position:50% align:center
in my agenda.
See you around.

00:19:26.958 --> 00:19:28.585 position:50% align:center
- Wait, what?
- Little old me's got some stuff

00:19:28.668 --> 00:19:29.878 position:50% align:center
to deal with, too.
- Uh...

00:19:32.422 --> 00:19:34.841 position:50% align:center
Man, they're busy.
[distant car horn honking]

00:19:37.927 --> 00:19:39.220 position:50% align:center
Been a while.

00:19:39.304 --> 00:19:40.889 position:50% align:center
Here for the first time
in a long time and it feels

00:19:40.972 --> 00:19:42.098 position:50% align:center
a bit different now.

00:19:42.182 --> 00:19:43.266 position:50% align:center
- Matter of fact they changed

00:19:43.350 --> 00:19:44.517 position:50% align:center
the sign about three months ago.
- [gasps]

00:19:44.601 --> 00:19:45.769 position:50% align:center
Chikuwa!

00:19:45.852 --> 00:19:47.145 position:50% align:center
- You're calling me by
my nickname?

00:19:47.228 --> 00:19:48.772 position:50% align:center
You know that's
an unpleasant thing to do.

00:19:48.855 --> 00:19:49.981 position:50% align:center
Use my real name.

00:19:50.065 --> 00:19:51.941 position:50% align:center
It's Wataru Chikushi.

00:19:52.025 --> 00:19:53.526 position:50% align:center
I told you that when I
was setting you back

00:19:53.610 --> 00:19:55.028 position:50% align:center
on the right path.

00:19:55.111 --> 00:19:57.197 position:50% align:center
- I really gave you a lot
of trouble back then, huh?

00:19:57.280 --> 00:19:58.448 position:50% align:center
- It was nothing.

00:19:58.531 --> 00:19:59.407 position:50% align:center
Hands out of your pockets,
though.

00:19:59.491 --> 00:20:00.825 position:50% align:center
- Well, anyway,

00:20:00.909 --> 00:20:02.786 position:50% align:center
what does a S.A.R.G.
inspector want with me?

00:20:02.869 --> 00:20:05.538 position:50% align:center
- Don't you call out to someone
you recognize on the street?

00:20:05.622 --> 00:20:07.957 position:50% align:center
- Oh, yeah. When you put it
like that, it does make sense.

00:20:08.041 --> 00:20:09.501 position:50% align:center
- While I've got you, Shu,

00:20:09.584 --> 00:20:11.670 position:50% align:center
how much do you know about
the group DoRed?

00:20:11.753 --> 00:20:13.296 position:50% align:center
- Nothing.
- Hold on, wait.

00:20:13.380 --> 00:20:15.173 position:50% align:center
Why you gotta be so heartless?

00:20:15.256 --> 00:20:18.134 position:50% align:center
So, still interact
with Ran Akage these days?

00:20:18.218 --> 00:20:19.969 position:50% align:center
- I'm afraid not.
- [grunts]

00:20:20.053 --> 00:20:22.305 position:50% align:center
Shuta, don't run away from me!

00:20:22.389 --> 00:20:25.600 position:50% align:center
[techno music]

00:20:25.684 --> 00:20:28.186 position:50% align:center
Just find you at Itadaki one
of these days!

00:20:28.269 --> 00:20:29.979 position:50% align:center
You're gonna have
to tell me your story!

00:20:30.063 --> 00:20:32.023 position:50% align:center
- This is ridiculous.
What's up with all that?

00:20:32.107 --> 00:20:34.984 position:50% align:center
Oh, boy.
Did Ran do something again?

00:20:35.819 --> 00:20:37.278 position:50% align:center
- Everything up to spec?

00:20:37.362 --> 00:20:38.988 position:50% align:center
- Yes, how is it?
How's it look?

00:20:39.072 --> 00:20:41.741 position:50% align:center
- I got good reception.
No complaints here.

00:20:41.825 --> 00:20:44.327 position:50% align:center
Looks like we'll get
good footage here.

00:20:44.411 --> 00:20:45.870 position:50% align:center
Okay, I'm counting on you.

00:20:45.954 --> 00:20:47.455 position:50% align:center
- Hey, Ran?
- Hmm?

00:20:47.539 --> 00:20:49.290 position:50% align:center
- I got intel
from Kunai they increased

00:20:49.374 --> 00:20:51.167 position:50% align:center
the quantity
of their security personnel.

00:20:51.251 --> 00:20:54.087 position:50% align:center
- Huh, so I guess not everybody
in S.A.R.G. is dumb.

00:20:54.170 --> 00:20:55.964 position:50% align:center
- Please tell me we're not gonna
get doxxed.

00:20:56.047 --> 00:20:58.049 position:50% align:center
Ran, if you end up
getting arrested--

00:20:58.133 --> 00:20:59.634 position:50% align:center
- You know what sort
of hacking techniques

00:20:59.718 --> 00:21:01.302 position:50% align:center
little old me has,
don't ya?

00:21:01.386 --> 00:21:03.805 position:50% align:center
- I know but please consider
the risks this time.

00:21:05.348 --> 00:21:06.933 position:50% align:center
- Listen, I don't like it,
either.

00:21:07.017 --> 00:21:09.686 position:50% align:center
Gori Suido's proposed
policies claim

00:21:09.769 --> 00:21:11.938 position:50% align:center
that rigorous societal control
will provide

00:21:12.022 --> 00:21:13.982 position:50% align:center
a more stable lifestyle
for everybody.

00:21:14.065 --> 00:21:15.692 position:50% align:center
It's only lip service.

00:21:15.775 --> 00:21:18.236 position:50% align:center
They added bias
to the Hazard Cast numbers,

00:21:18.319 --> 00:21:21.489 position:50% align:center
and minorities are hunted down
without any reasonable cause.

00:21:21.573 --> 00:21:23.658 position:50% align:center
- The other day the S.A.R.G.
were doing just that

00:21:23.742 --> 00:21:25.243 position:50% align:center
over in Shantytown.

00:21:25.326 --> 00:21:26.828 position:50% align:center
- Those guys simply
get desperate

00:21:26.911 --> 00:21:28.830 position:50% align:center
and resort to committing crimes.

00:21:28.913 --> 00:21:32.042 position:50% align:center
Who's the one really disrupting
the peace down in Shantytown?

00:21:32.125 --> 00:21:34.961 position:50% align:center
We're not gonna let that fly
or play by this guy's rules.

00:21:35.045 --> 00:21:37.422 position:50% align:center
- Right.
- Well, contact you later.

00:21:37.505 --> 00:21:38.590 position:50% align:center
- Okay.

00:21:38.673 --> 00:21:41.593 position:50% align:center
[birds chirping]

00:21:45.388 --> 00:21:47.015 position:50% align:center
- Oh, crap, crap.

00:21:50.393 --> 00:21:52.103 position:50% align:center
- It ought to be somewhere
around here.

00:21:52.187 --> 00:21:53.188 position:50% align:center
[gasps]

00:21:53.688 --> 00:21:54.856 position:50% align:center
This is it.

00:21:55.440 --> 00:21:57.525 position:50% align:center
The other one's located right
over there

00:21:57.609 --> 00:21:59.444 position:50% align:center
and it's been painted over
basically like saying

00:21:59.527 --> 00:22:01.279 position:50% align:center
they'll be committing
a crime here.

00:22:01.363 --> 00:22:03.239 position:50% align:center
The number of cameras
that are vandalized

00:22:03.323 --> 00:22:04.741 position:50% align:center
has been increasing lately.

00:22:04.824 --> 00:22:07.202 position:50% align:center
Is it resistance
against Hazard Cast?

00:22:07.827 --> 00:22:10.080 position:50% align:center
I suppose I'll send
a confirmation report

00:22:10.163 --> 00:22:12.207 position:50% align:center
to the management division.
[grunts]

00:22:12.957 --> 00:22:14.000 position:50% align:center
[exhales]

00:22:14.084 --> 00:22:15.377 position:50% align:center
Just my imagination.

00:22:18.922 --> 00:22:22.634 position:50% align:center
- ♪ Mon, Mon, Mon,
Mon Jungle ♪

00:22:22.717 --> 00:22:24.969 position:50% align:center
♪ Mon, Mon, Mon, Mon Jungle ♪

00:22:25.053 --> 00:22:28.264 position:50% align:center
- Oh, let's go to Mon Jungle!
- Yes, please!

00:22:28.348 --> 00:22:31.309 position:50% align:center
- It's crazy how surreal
the Mon Jungle commercial is.

00:22:31.393 --> 00:22:33.478 position:50% align:center
Dealing with Chikuwa
made me hungry.

00:22:33.561 --> 00:22:35.271 position:50% align:center
- Now time to fill up
my stomach before

00:22:35.355 --> 00:22:37.148 position:50% align:center
the war begins.
- Monjayaki, huh?

00:22:37.232 --> 00:22:38.400 position:50% align:center
No.

00:22:38.483 --> 00:22:40.360 position:50% align:center
all: Okonomiyaki!

00:22:40.443 --> 00:22:41.695 position:50% align:center
- [groans]

00:22:41.778 --> 00:22:43.822 position:50% align:center
- These guys again?
- Just my luck.

00:22:43.905 --> 00:22:47.242 position:50% align:center
- Oh, R.G.B.
So you're all here, huh?

00:22:47.325 --> 00:22:48.493 position:50% align:center
You're earlier than I planned.
- Wait, what?

00:22:48.576 --> 00:22:49.661 position:50% align:center
- Oh, give me a break, Mari.

00:22:49.744 --> 00:22:52.664 position:50% align:center
[sizzling]

00:22:53.707 --> 00:22:54.833 position:50% align:center
- [grunts]
Shuta,

00:22:54.916 --> 00:22:56.292 position:50% align:center
you're invading my territory.

00:22:56.376 --> 00:22:57.502 position:50% align:center
Keep yours to the edge.
- Huh?

00:22:57.585 --> 00:22:58.837 position:50% align:center
If I get any closer to the edge,

00:22:58.920 --> 00:23:00.296 position:50% align:center
the thing will lose its shape,
Koki.

00:23:00.380 --> 00:23:01.548 position:50% align:center
You need to get closer!

00:23:01.631 --> 00:23:03.049 position:50% align:center
[both snarling]

00:23:03.133 --> 00:23:05.051 position:50% align:center
- Hey, both of you,
stop arguing this instant!

00:23:05.135 --> 00:23:07.554 position:50% align:center
- [mimics rocket noises]

00:23:07.637 --> 00:23:09.139 position:50% align:center
- How much are you pouring on?

00:23:09.222 --> 00:23:10.932 position:50% align:center
You turned it into
a mayo pancake!

00:23:11.016 --> 00:23:12.976 position:50% align:center
- Bonito flakes, tasty.

00:23:13.059 --> 00:23:14.185 position:50% align:center
Oh, and then last but not least,

00:23:14.269 --> 00:23:17.564 position:50% align:center
sprinkle on some seaweed.
Finished!

00:23:17.647 --> 00:23:19.858 position:50% align:center
- Ah, that thing!
- How dexterous.

00:23:19.941 --> 00:23:21.860 position:50% align:center
- Photogenic, right?

00:23:21.943 --> 00:23:23.486 position:50% align:center
- Looks like it would easily
go viral.

00:23:23.570 --> 00:23:25.321 position:50% align:center
- I'm gonna start feeling like
it's too good to eat,

00:23:25.405 --> 00:23:26.781 position:50% align:center
so stop it.
- [scoffs]

00:23:26.865 --> 00:23:30.952 position:50% align:center
Anything possessing form
or shape eventually breaks.

00:23:31.036 --> 00:23:31.995 position:50% align:center
[both shouting]

00:23:32.078 --> 00:23:33.246 position:50% align:center
- Then cut it up.
♪ Cut it up ♪

00:23:33.329 --> 00:23:35.123 position:50% align:center
- No hesitation!
- [chomps]

00:23:35.206 --> 00:23:37.375 position:50% align:center
Graffiti is art destined
from the very moment

00:23:37.459 --> 00:23:39.210 position:50% align:center
