to be erased someday.

00:23:39.294 --> 00:23:40.795 position:50% align:center
[gulps]
And that's precisely why

00:23:40.879 --> 00:23:42.297 position:50% align:center
street art resonates
with you emotionally

00:23:42.380 --> 00:23:43.715 position:50% align:center
when you see it.
- Ran,

00:23:43.798 --> 00:23:45.467 position:50% align:center
you're like a seaside Picasso.
- Sea?

00:23:45.550 --> 00:23:46.468 position:50% align:center
- So enlighten me.
- Who?

00:23:46.551 --> 00:23:47.552 position:50% align:center
- Is that why you started DoRed?

00:23:47.635 --> 00:23:49.763 position:50% align:center
- Ah, let's see.
- Here we go.

00:23:49.846 --> 00:23:50.972 position:50% align:center
- I don't remember.

00:23:51.056 --> 00:23:52.849 position:50% align:center
It was quite a while ago
I started it up.

00:23:52.932 --> 00:23:54.476 position:50% align:center
- I wanted to ask as well.

00:23:54.559 --> 00:23:56.644 position:50% align:center
You're seeking more members
on the 'net, right?

00:23:56.728 --> 00:23:58.480 position:50% align:center
This thing is called DoRed?
- [singing]

00:23:58.563 --> 00:24:01.232 position:50% align:center
- Chikuwa from the S.A.R.G.
asked me about you earlier.

00:24:01.316 --> 00:24:03.151 position:50% align:center
- I'm sorry to trouble you.

00:24:03.234 --> 00:24:06.613 position:50% align:center
It's true that the S.A.R.G.
has had their eyes on us lately.

00:24:06.696 --> 00:24:07.989 position:50% align:center
How about you, Ko?

00:24:08.073 --> 00:24:09.282 position:50% align:center
Are you lending Daddy Gori

00:24:09.366 --> 00:24:11.076 position:50% align:center
a helping hand while going
to college?

00:24:11.159 --> 00:24:13.244 position:50% align:center
- I have my own thoughts
concerning these matters.

00:24:13.328 --> 00:24:14.829 position:50% align:center
That's why I'm interning
at S.A.R.G. presently.

00:24:14.913 --> 00:24:16.373 position:50% align:center
- Huh?
Really, Koki?

00:24:16.456 --> 00:24:18.208 position:50% align:center
You're gonna join S.A.R.G.?
- Not a chance.

00:24:18.291 --> 00:24:19.959 position:50% align:center
I want to become a politician.

00:24:20.502 --> 00:24:22.295 position:50% align:center
The Special Administrative
Region Guard

00:24:22.379 --> 00:24:24.881 position:50% align:center
is a police organization funded
by the Suido Zaibatsu.

00:24:24.964 --> 00:24:26.549 position:50% align:center
So, yeah,
it was easy to join 'em.

00:24:26.633 --> 00:24:27.759 position:50% align:center
More importantly,

00:24:27.842 --> 00:24:29.511 position:50% align:center
they deal with Hazard Cast.

00:24:29.594 --> 00:24:31.763 position:50% align:center
The place is chock full
of stuff I want to learn about.

00:24:31.846 --> 00:24:34.015 position:50% align:center
- I prefer to hack
into real life with art,

00:24:34.099 --> 00:24:36.309 position:50% align:center
and the real world
is operated based upon

00:24:36.393 --> 00:24:38.186 position:50% align:center
a certain set of rules
and principles.

00:24:38.269 --> 00:24:40.563 position:50% align:center
Whip!
And those rules are created by

00:24:40.647 --> 00:24:42.982 position:50% align:center
