as a whole.

00:24:47.821 --> 00:24:49.406 position:50% align:center
- But that art you draw
is unauthorized, right?

00:24:49.489 --> 00:24:51.199 position:50% align:center
- It's called street art, Shu.

00:24:51.658 --> 00:24:53.159 position:50% align:center
- Damage to property
and buildings,

00:24:53.243 --> 00:24:54.452 position:50% align:center
quite a misdemeanor.

00:24:54.536 --> 00:24:56.454 position:50% align:center
If you go too far,
you'll be arrested.

00:24:56.538 --> 00:24:58.039 position:50% align:center
- Arrested by you, Ko?

00:24:58.123 --> 00:25:00.333 position:50% align:center
Because of the political crime
of illegal art?

