The 24th ward's
in a transition period

00:25:02.752 --> 00:25:04.921 position:50% align:center
with the incorporation
into Tokyo approaching.

00:25:05.005 --> 00:25:06.923 position:50% align:center
Doesn't the S.A.R.G. have
more important work to do?

00:25:07.007 --> 00:25:09.134 position:50% align:center
- Discipline's important,
especially in a transition.

00:25:09.217 --> 00:25:10.927 position:50% align:center
- But who exactly
is that discipline for

00:25:11.011 --> 00:25:12.345 position:50% align:center
and who does it benefit?
- [grunts]

00:25:12.429 --> 00:25:14.055 position:50% align:center
- You two really put a lot
of thought into this

00:25:14.139 --> 00:25:15.682 position:50% align:center
and are acting accordingly, huh?

00:25:15.765 --> 00:25:17.851 position:50% align:center
- Yeah, you two
are like fully grown adults.

00:25:17.934 --> 00:25:20.270 position:50% align:center
Totally different from Shu here.
- [groans]

00:25:20.353 --> 00:25:21.688 position:50% align:center
[both groaning]

00:25:21.771 --> 00:25:23.189 position:50% align:center
- Hold on.
